extends ../layout

block content
  .container.container-clean.pb0.mb20(style='position:relative;')
    //- div(style='position:absolute;left:-25px;top:-10px;')
      img(src='./img/phlogo.png', width='100')
    .row.mb20
      .col-sm-push-1.col-sm-10.align-center
        h1.mt0.mb10.lato.lato900 Promote your products on popular blogs, and increase revenue
        p.m0.lato.lato400 100% of traffic goes to people who are interested in your product

  .container.container-fix
    .row.pb20.pt20
      .col-sm-4.align-center
        .clearfix
          i.fa.fa-rss.fa-4x.notimp
        h2.mb10 Top Bloggers
        p.m0 Build your profile and <u class="lato700">deliver daily products recommendations</u> to your readers. It's easy & free.
      .col-sm-4.align-center
        .clearfix
          i.fa.fa-bullhorn.fa-4x.notimp
        h2.mb10 Promote
        p.m0 Increase engagement in your blog, <u class="lato700">give your user one place to find & buy</u> the best products.
      .col-sm-4.align-center
        .clearfix
          i.fa.fa-shopping-cart.fa-4x.notimp
        h2.mb10 Sell
        p.m0 You recommend products and we deliver sponsored links to each of them. <u class="lato700">You earn 70% on every campaign</u>.

  .container.container-clean
    .row.mb15.mt40
      .col-sm-12.align-center
        form.form-inline(action='/signup', role='form', method='post')
          input(type='hidden', name='_csrf', value=_csrf)
          .form-group
            .input-group.pr10
              input.form-control.input-lg(type='email', name='email', id='email', placeholder='Email', autofocus, autocomplete='off')
          .form-group
            .input-group.pr10
              input.form-control.input-lg(type='password', name='password', id='password', placeholder='Password', autocomplete='off')
          .form-group
            .input-group.pr10
              input.form-control.input-lg(type='password', name='confirmPassword', id='confirmPassword', placeholder='Confirm Password', autocomplete='off')
          .form-group
            .input-group
              button.btn.btn-danger.btn-lg(type='submit') Get started
        p.mb0.mt15.lato.lato400.small Please read out <a href="">Term of Service</a>.


  .container.container-fix.pb0.mb20
    .row.mb10
      .col-sm-12
        small.imp FEATURED BLOGGERS
    .row
      .col-sm-12
        include ../grid.blogs.jade


  .container.container-clean.pb0.mb20(style='position:relative;')
    .row.mb20
      .col-sm-push-1.col-sm-10.align-center
        h1.mt0.mb10.lato.lato900 How it works
        p.m0.lato.lato400 In a few simple steps you will be able to start earning money

  .container.container-fix
    .row
      .col-sm-1.align-right
        i.fa.fa-angle-double-right.fa-4x.notimp
      .col-sm-3
        h5 Blogger recommends
        p.m0 Register today and start delivering products recommendation to your readers.
      .col-sm-1.align-right
        i.fa.fa-angle-double-right.fa-4x.notimp
      .col-sm-3
        h5 You add sponsored link
        p.m0 We need only few minutes to confirm your profile as a verified blogger.
      .col-sm-1.align-right
        i.fa.fa-angle-double-right.fa-4x.notimp
      .col-sm-3
        h5 Increase traffic & sales
        p.m0 Update your profile with daily recommendations. This way you increase chance to have more active campaign.


  .container.container-clean.pb0.mb20(style='position:relative;')
    .row.mb20
      .col-sm-push-1.col-sm-10.align-center
        h1.mt0.mb10.lato.lato900 Why
        p.m0.lato.lato400 Our main goal is to increase your revenue by delivering your products to right place & people.

  .container.container-fix
    .row
      .col-sm-12
        ul.m0
          li
            h5 Deliver only to right people
            p.m0 Many ad networks deliver random content, often not incontext to your blog.
          li
            h5 Don't live unanswerd question: "Where to buy this product?"
            p.m0 Your readers often ask you where to buy products you write in your posts? Out widget is very handy place to deliver this answer.
          li
            h5 Find more about how popular is your product
            p.m0 We deliver great insights about products you recommend. Now you will learn more witch products are the most popular.
          li
            h5 Find the best bloggers
            p.m0 We take care on looking for new adverstisers, who will add sponsored links to each of your recommendations.

  .container.container-clean.pb0.mb20(style='position:relative;')
    .row.mb20
      .col-sm-push-1.col-sm-10.align-center
        h1.mt0.mb10.lato.lato900 Start selling today

    .row.mb15
      .col-sm-12.align-center
        a.btn.btn-danger.btn-lg(href='/signup') SIGN UP FOR FREE

  .container

    section.mt50
      h3.m0 FAQ
      hr

      h4 I'm blogger. How ShopByBlog works for me?
      p Product Hunt surfaces the best new products, every day. It's a place for product-loving enthusiasts to share and geek out about the latest mobile apps, websites, hardware projects, and tech creations.

      p You can read more about our story on <a href="http://pando.com/2013/12/04/can-the-democratic-power-of-a-platform-like-hacker-news-be-applied-to-products/" target="_blank">PandoDaily</a>, <a href="http://www.fastcolabs.com/3023152/open-company/the-wisdom-of-the-20-minute-startup" target="_blank">Fast Company</a>, <a href="http://techcrunch.com/2014/06/04/product-hunt-is-the-social-news-site-of-tech-products-read-by-influential-people/" target="_blank">TechCrunch</a>, <a href="http://thenextweb.com/insider/2014/06/05/product-hunt-is-leveling-the-playing-field-to-help-good-apps-and-startups-get-attention/" target="_blank">The Next Web</a>, <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/product-hunt-2014-6" target="_blank">Business Insider</a>, <a href="http://www.foxbusiness.com/on-air/risk-and-reward/index.html#/v/3639940132001" target="_blank">Fox Business</a>, and <a href="http://www.forbes.com/sites/sethporges/2014/07/03/the-creator-of-product-hunt-spills-the-hit-sites-dirty-details" target="_blank">Forbes</a>.</p>

    section
      h4 How much I can earn?
      p You get 60% and we 40% of each deals we'll setup.

      ul
        li URL - Direct link to the product page (avoid links to press or blogs)
        li Product Name
        li Tagline - Very short description of the product (make it catchy!)

  .container.container-clean.pb0.mb20(style='position:relative;')
    .row.mb20
      .col-sm-push-1.col-sm-10.align-center
        h1.mt0.mb10.lato.lato900 Have a question? Write us!

    .row.mb15
      .col-sm-12.align-center
        a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(href='/signup') info@shopbyblog.com

